{"comments":"Neumorphism - soft UI / \"soft glass\" effect compound.\n\nNeumorphism creates a soft, extruded plastic appearance using\ndual shadows (light and dark) to simulate depth on a uniform\nbackground. Popular in 2019-2020 UI trends.\n\n## Visual Effect\n\n- Light shadow on one side (simulates light source reflection)\n- Dark shadow on opposite side (simulates cast shadow)\n- Background color matches parent (crucial for the effect)\n- Creates \"soft\" raised or inset appearance\n\n## Variants\n\n- **Raised**: Element appears to protrude from surface\n- **Inset**: Element appears pressed into surface\n- **Flat**: Subtle, almost imperceptible depth\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Color.RGB\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Bounded\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[76,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/Neumorphism.purs","start":[76,3]},"title":"Raised"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[77,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/Neumorphism.purs","start":[77,3]},"title":"Inset"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[78,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/Neumorphism.purs","start":[78,3]},"title":"Flat"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[79,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/Neumorphism.purs","start":[79,3]},"title":"Concave"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[80,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/Neumorphism.purs","start":[80,3]},"title":"Convex"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","S